in Shropshire With Ford dealerships in Shrewsbury, Oswestry and Telford, Furrows has
the widest choice of new and approved used vehicles in Shropshire. Visit one of our showrooms or find out about the full range of Ford
models and services here on our website. 
From Fiesta to Focus, and Kuga to Mustang, we have them all, together
with bespoke finance options and excellent customer service. We also specialise in commercial vehicle sales through our Ford Transit
centre in Shrewsbury, providing ever light commercial sales and expert
servicing to help keep your vehicles on the road and productive. Kia, Skoda and Mazda​​ At Furrows we are also main dealers for Kia, Skoda and Mazda. Check out our new car deals and options, offering you everything from a small city car to SUVs,  sports and executive models. And we have an extensive range of approved used cars at each of our locations in Shrewsbury, Telford and Oswestry too. We can arrange offers for your car finance, tailored to your specific budget and repayment preferences.​ Motability, servicing and spares In addition to new and used sales, we provide a comprehensive aftersales service.  Servicing, accident repairs, MOT, replacement tyres and parts are available for every Ford, Kia, Skoda and Mazda model, helping you keep your vehicle warranty up-to-date and maintain your car’s value. Every Furrows technician is fully trained to the highest standards and we use only genuine manufacturer parts and the latest diagnostics in our servicing and repairs. Our great value service plans can help you budget for the cost too. Our highly-trained team of Motability advisers can offer you complete and impartial advice to help you make the right vehicle and leasing decision for you.        Contact Us     Enquire Now     Book a Service     Back to Top              Back    Vehicle Valuation      Compare Saved Vehicles      Top          Close            Welcome to Furrows Group. To optimise your experience, cookie settings on the website are set to allow all cookies. By continuing your journey throughout the website, you consent to this. You can change these settings here.   Change Settings  Accept    Find out more about cookies         Strictly Necessary  Strictly Necessary cookies are essential to let you move around the website and use its features, such as accessing secure areas, shopping baskets and online billing. These cookies allow our website to provide services at your request.      Disabled - Performance Cookies  Performance cookies collect information